## Common Usage Patterns

{% if action == 'list' %}
### List all resources in default namespace

```bash
xcsh {{ group }} {{ action }} <resource-type>
```

### List resources in a specific namespace

```bash
xcsh {{ group }} {{ action }} <resource-type> -n example-namespace
```

### List with JSON output

```bash
xcsh {{ group }} {{ action }} <resource-type> --output-format json
```
{% elif action == 'get' %}
### Get resource details

```bash
