```

### Get with YAML output

```bash
xcsh {{ group }} {{ action }} <resource-type> <name> --output-format yaml
```

### Get resource in specific namespace

```bash
xcsh {{ group }} {{ action }} <resource-type> <name> -n example-namespace
```
